	dprr:hasNoteText "CIL 6.1374, and 1375-ILS 917, 917a. See PIR(2) 2.151f., no. 686. Probably not the Praetor of 44. Died before 12 B. C." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6621> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6621" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. - Held office in the late Republic or Early Augustan age, and died before 12 B.C. (CIL 6.1374-ILS 917). See PIR(2) 2.151, no. 686, where Epulo is interpreted as a priesthood, not a cognomen." .
